snippet.title: Biomutant - gamescom 2018 Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
This year's gamescom is officially here and so is a new, insane gameplay trailer for Biomutant!

Combine Mutant Powers, Bionics and Weapons in this original Action RPG, coming 2018! Explore a world in turmoil and define its fate – will you be the hero and saviour or lead it to an even darker destiny?
